---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contato | Engenharia da Conversão">
	<section class="min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center px-6 md:px-20 lg:px-40 bg-darkBg pt-32 pb-20">
		<span class="text-brandCyan font-space text-xs md:text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-8">Engenharia da Conversão</span>
		<h1 class="font-sora text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-textPrimary leading-[1.05] mb-8">
			Descubra onde sua operação está perdendo dinheiro.
		</h1>
		<p class="font-sora text-lg md:text-xl text-textSecondary max-w-2xl leading-relaxed mb-16">
			Análises indicam que 71% das empresas falham por falta de método, não de tecnologia. Vamos fazer uma auditoria de 30 minutos para mapear e eliminar os atritos do seu negócio.
		</p>
		
		<div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-4 mb-24 bg-surface p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 w-full max-w-xl">
			<a href="#" onclick="Calendly.initPopupWidget({url: 'https://calendly.com/nathanborges546/30min'});return false;" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-brandCyan text-darkBg font-space font-medium tracking-wide uppercase rounded-xl hover:bg-brandCyan/90 transition-transform hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 w-full sm:w-auto">
				Garantir Minha Auditoria Gratuita
			</a>
			<p class="text-textSecondary/60 font-space text-xs tracking-wide">
				* Garantia de conformidade com GEO e otimização de INP inferior a 200ms.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-auto pt-10 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-8">
			<a href="/" class="text-textSecondary hover:text-textPrimary transition-colors font-space text-sm">← Voltar para Home</a>
			
			<div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-textSecondary font-space text-sm">
				<a href="https://wa.me/5564993335277" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-brandCyan transition-colors">WhatsApp</a>
				<a href="https://www.instagram.com/nathanb.exe/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-brandCyan transition-colors">Instagram</a>
				<a href="https://www.behance.net/nathanborges546" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-brandCyan transition-colors">Behance</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
